{"tid":181962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳啟宗：香港樓市「20幾年來最好就係今日」　稱梁以外無人能控制樓價","createTime":"2017-04-01T04:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T02:37:38.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5466588b6e6586e21bda0b0eca947e98e748b50","tid":181962,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"被外界視為「梁粉」的恒隆地產主席陳啟宗，今日受訪時不點名暗批曾俊華是完全沒有為明日着想的「守財奴」，亦同時開口大讚梁振英「做得好」。他指梁在任時增加土地供應量，令香港房地產市場20多年來首次受控，更表示「邊個能夠將樓價控制住，邊個就爲香港做了一件好大的事」，直言除了梁振英外，「我看不到有第二個人可以做到」。"},{"pid":"e45166d417d5f2c43889f105bc23e26e477735e9","tid":181962,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"一個地產商講呢番說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不停升緊係最好啦"},{"pid":"df554eecad9322b697dcb959f58b93ffccf57157","tid":181962,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個地產商講呢番說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不停升緊係最好啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e56d95b50ccbb66dd794e4d82ca5660bf54273","tid":181962,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"美國人陳啟宗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213e5d73e3096efb72c3a1bf6c920a75cc38130e","tid":181962,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"依啲說話真係4月1號先講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bcd94a34b0c91bc783009c549ca0d87c8941ed","tid":181962,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:28:47.000Z","msg":